description:
Requirements:
• Solid front-end development skills: React, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, JSON;
• Solid Back end development skills: . Net framework, . Net Core, C#
• Familiar with CSS pre-processing platforms, such as Sass, LESS, or Stylus;
• Understanding responsive design principles and how to implement them on the coding side;
• Proficient in common development tools such as Git, Npm, Gulp/WebPack, and JSLint;
• Experience in Agile development methodology and tools usage;
• Experienced in Visual Studio, C#, MVC/MVVM and Azure is a plus;
• Experience in devOps, CI/CD Pipe would be an advantage
• Solid front-end development skills: Angular, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, JSON;
• Solid Back end development skills: . Net framework, . Net Core, C#
• Experience in Agile development methodology and tools usage;
• Unit testing and testing approach ( development drive testing )
• Good command of the English language
• Experienced in Visual Studio, C#, MVC/MVVM and Azure is a plus;
•... Experience in devOps, CI/CD Pipe would be an advantage
• Very good communication skills
• Should be very interactive and top on deliverables being working from the client environment
• Ready to learn new tools and technology in related areas

